                <h3>Contact the Alambic team</h3>
                
                <p>The Alambic project is <b>open-source</b>, published under the <a href="https://www.eclipse.org/legal/epl-v10.html">Eclipse Public Licence</a>.</p>
		<p>The project is hosted on BitBucket at <a href="https://bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic">bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic</a>. You can find there the issue tracker, a wiki and the git repositories. Any contribution <a href="https://bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic/wiki/Help_Us/">is more than welcome</a>: use case, requirement, test, documentation, code or feedback! Since we invest quite some time in Alambic, we would definitely love to hear from you.</p>

		<p>The Alambic team can be contacted using the below contact web form, or at <code>alambic (at) castalia (dot) solutions</code>.</p>
		
